          %hr{noshade: "noshade", size: "4", width: "470px"}
        .answerTextBox2
          %p This is why these two products are structurally similar yay rainbow unicorns. I love mochi ice cream. This is why these two products are structurally similar yay rainbow unicorns. I love mochi ice cream. This is why these two products are structurally similar yay rainbow unicorns. I love mochi ice cream. 
          %hr{noshade: "noshade", size: "4", width: "470px"}
          
